P0.1 Plan Approval Implementation Notes
=====================================

Files Modified:
- internal/state/types.go: Added PlanStatusRejected constant
- internal/state/store.go: Added RejectPlan(), enhanced ApprovePlan() with state validation
- internal/providers/aws.go: Added aws_approve_plan tool, removed auto-approval from createInfra
- internal/state/store_test.go: 7 new tests for plan state transitions
- internal/providers/aws_test.go: 6 new tests for approval workflow

Key Design Decisions:
1. Idempotent operations: Approving an already-approved plan returns success
2. Terminal states: approved/rejected/expired cannot transition further
3. ErrInvalidState used for invalid transitions (rejected→approved, approved→rejected)
4. ErrPlanNotApproved wired into createInfra for clear error messages

